HEADWORD: Inframedian
<hw>In`fra*me"di*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Infra</ets> + <ets>median</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zoological
Geog.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the interval or zone along the sea
bottom, at the depth of between fifty and one hundred fathoms.</def>
<rj><au>E. Forbes.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
